Hi Ben,

The Solex PDSIT carbs were intended for 1972-74 buses with type4 
engines; and they were continued through 75-79 in other markets. I don't 
think they can be made to fit a type1 engine.

They were used with both manual and automatic transmissions.

Happy Trails,

